 795:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  * @brief This internal API sets door state detector configurations like remap setting,
 796:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  * calibration threshold and init gyro bias configuration.
 797:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *
 798:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  * @param[in]      config      : Structure instance of bmi2_door_state_detector_config.
 799:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  * @param[in, out] dev         : Structure instance of bmi2_dev.
 800:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *
 801:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  * @verbatim
 802:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 803:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *  bmi2_door_state_detector_config  |
 804:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *  Structure parameters             |                   Description
 805:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *-----------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------
 806:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *                                   | Axis remap status:
 807:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *  remap flag                       | 0: undone, Axis remap needs to be done by the user
 808:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *                                   | 1: done, Axis remap is set in register
 809:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *                                   | Default value is 0.
 810:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  * ----------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
 811:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *                                   | Map the desired axis sign to z axis:
 812:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *  z sign                           | 0: invert, Invert the axis sign
 813:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *                                   | 1: not_invert, Do not invert the axis sign
 814:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *                                   | Default value is 0.
 815:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  * ----------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
 816:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *                                   | Map the desired axis to z axis:
 817:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *                                   | 0：x_axis, Map x axis to z-axis
 818:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *  z axis                           | 1: y_axis, Map y axis to z-axis
 819:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *                                   | 2: z_axis, Map z axis to z-axis
 820:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *                                   | Default value is 0.
 821:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  * ----------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
 822:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *  init_calib_thr                   | Initial calibration threshold.
 823:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *                                   | Default value is 20.
 824:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  * ----------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
 825:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *                                   | Manual reset enable:
 826:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *  reset_enable_flag                | 0: disable.
 827:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *                                   | 1: enable. This bit will be set to 0 after reset is done.
 828:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *                                   | Default value is 0.
