1036:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *                          | Default value is 0xAA = 83mg.
1037:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
1038:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *  x_sel, y_sel, z_sel     |  Selects the feature on a per-axis basis
1039:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
1040:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  * @endverbatim
1041:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *
1042:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  * @return Result of API execution status
1043:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  * @retval 0 -> Success
1044:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  * @retval < 0 -> Fail
1045:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  */
