1154:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c **** /*!
1155:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *  @brief This API:
1156:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *  1) Updates the device structure with address of the configuration file.
1157:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *  2) Initializes BMI270_DSD sensor.
1158:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *  3) Writes the configuration file.
1159:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *  4) Updates the feature offset parameters in the device structure.
1160:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_dsd.c ****  *  5) Updates the maximum number of pages, in the device structure.
